articles.author: Lucia Mutikani
articles.title: US weekly jobless claims at three-month high; import prices tumble - Reuters
articles.description: The number of Americans filing new claims for unemployment benefits increased to a three-month high last week, suggesting that labor market conditions continued to ease, which could help the Federal Reserve's fight against inflation.
